* 2019年（平成31年）3月23日：[[宮古站|宮古站]]至[[釜石站|釜石站]]之間重開，同時三陸鐵道繼承該區段<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.sanrikutetsudou.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/959ef58e3e516fa24592aaf135f5681d.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-22 |archive-date=2019-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014155005/https://www.sanrikutetsudou.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/959ef58e3e516fa24592aaf135f5681d.pdf }}</ref>。同時此站啟用<ref name="sanriku10129"/><ref name="mainichi20180329"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www3.nhk.or.jp/lnews/morioka/20180404/6040000527.html |title=三陸鉄道 １４駅の愛称決まる |publisher=日本放送協会 |accessdate=2018-04-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180410055337/http://www3.nhk.or.jp/lnews/morioka/20180404/6040000527.html |archivedate=2018-04-10 |language=ja }}</ref>。

